Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.07,0:21:03.49,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}純真さが シンプルな力に 変わる 世界に影をつくりだす
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.14,0:21:18.03,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}ガラスケ一スに横たわる 光の存在に触れたくても
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.11,0:21:25.13,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}振り上げた手 降ろせなくて
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.50,0:21:33.80,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}落ちるようにしゃがみこんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.93,0:21:42.12,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}Prototype boy 明日の理想だけで
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.36,0:21:49.61,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}語り継ぐような 美談にもならないけど
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.82,0:21:56.94,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}この体を失いそうな
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.14,0:22:06.11,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}ギリギリの場所が 哀しいくらい似合ってる
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.07,0:21:03.49,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}当纯真变为单纯的力量 世界由此诞生了影子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.14,0:21:18.03,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}穿透过玻璃橱 感触着这光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.11,0:21:25.13,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}举起的手无法放下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.50,0:21:33.80,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}却如同坠落般跌下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.93,0:21:42.12,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}Prototype boy 抛开明天的理想
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.36,0:21:49.61,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}即便无法成为传承的美谈
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.82,0:21:56.94,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}如同就要失去这副身躯一般
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.14,0:22:06.11,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}在极限的边缘 跌入悲伤的深渊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,----Dialogue

Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.93,0:00:10.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么? 这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.31,0:00:12.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那架机体是!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.74,0:00:13.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,声音?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.28,0:00:15.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事!?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.96,0:00:17.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能听到声音…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.90,0:00:20.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这里的人们的声音…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.30,0:00:22.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.36,0:00:23.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊! 那声音是…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.41,0:00:26.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道是 露易丝!?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.45,0:00:28.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露易丝!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.84,0:00:31.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么!? 为什么沙慈的声音…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.80,0:00:34.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露易丝… 难道在MS里…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.73,0:00:36.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙慈! 你在哪里?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.47,0:00:37.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙慈! 在哪…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.80,0:00:39.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道在 Gundam里…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.41,0:00:43.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露易丝 难道你现在是A-LAWS…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.92,0:00:46.06,Second,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听我说 能把我的梦想托付给沙慈吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.06,0:00:47.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙慈 为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.77,0:00:49.74,Second,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到宇宙去
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.15,0:00:51.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么 你会…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.78,0:00:52.88,Second,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实现梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.24,0:00:54.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.08,0:00:56.28,Second,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是我的梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.31,0:00:58.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么 你会…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.48,0:01:01.61,Second,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 让我的梦想实现吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.73,0:01:04.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么你会在这里啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.80,0:01:08.89,Second,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙慈… 我们约好了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.97,0:03:28.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙慈!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.52,0:03:30.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露易丝!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.43,0:03:36.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此路不通
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.45,0:03:40.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挡我者死
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.30,0:03:57.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.64,0:03:59.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.25,0:04:15.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.66,0:04:30.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是增援吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.81,0:04:34.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种情况下 不能使用TRANS-AM
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.58,0:04:41.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,注意后方 注意后方
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.54,0:04:41.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么!?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.30,0:04:46.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了大佐的胜利
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.65,0:04:53.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是现在
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.50,0:04:59.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Cherudim…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.49,0:05:02.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.23,0:05:05.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底怎么了?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.14,0:05:15.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.39,0:05:17.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,合体成功了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.18,0:05:19.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,00 Raiser
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.53,0:05:25.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,压缩粒子 填充完毕
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.19,0:05:25.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这声音
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.12,0:05:33.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这下就搞定你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.67,0:05:34.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新机型么？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.60,0:05:35.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有声音
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.96,0:05:42.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那里么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.86,0:05:49.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没完
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.33,0:06:00.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能… 不过 我是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.40,0:06:03.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,变革者
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.25,0:06:09.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.12,0:06:14.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.08,0:06:16.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那里
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.88,0:06:23.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别小看我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.85,0:06:41.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被打败了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.75,0:06:44.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为变革者的我…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.26,0:06:54.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到极限时间了么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.91,0:06:57.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 刚才那到底是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.58,0:07:01.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你干什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.75,0:07:03.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托密勒还没脱离危险
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.46,0:07:05.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.10,0:07:08.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.56,0:07:11.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到露易丝那里
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.26,0:07:13.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露易丝…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.65,0:07:20.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,机体量子化了!?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.53,0:07:24.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam居然隐藏了我所不知的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.15,0:07:27.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.83,0:07:29.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么有些惊慌的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.06,0:07:35.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闭嘴 你这臭婊子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.05,0:07:47.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 没有Gadessa怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.76,0:07:49.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撤退命令
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.16,0:07:57.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌人MS部队 开始撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.51,0:07:58.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托勒密 终止炮击
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.13,0:08:00.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam各机 保持警戒
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.89,0:08:01.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.34,0:08:04.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刹那那家伙 打下多少敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.30,0:08:06.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多10架吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.28,0:08:11.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别放松 我们还有破坏卫星武器的目标
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.58,0:08:14.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米蕾娜 我知道你担心着父母
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.63,0:08:17.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但还是麻烦你操作Karel维修托密勒和Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.96,0:08:18.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.56,0:08:20.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是Arios
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.72,0:08:22.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经将运输舰护送至安全区域
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.47,0:08:25.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米蕾娜 你妈妈安全了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.01,0:08:28.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 米蕾娜
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.62,0:08:31.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯嗯 我赶紧去忙维修
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.27,0:08:36.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,00 Raiser
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.21,0:08:39.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟有如此性能
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.41,0:08:46.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,动起来啊 求你了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.71,0:08:47.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙慈·库洛斯洛特
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.77,0:08:50.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快给我动起来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.32,0:08:59.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要去露易丝那里
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.91,0:09:08.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听到沙慈的声音了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.37,0:09:10.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙慈在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.78,0:09:13.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在天行者那里
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.80,0:09:17.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和杀害爸爸妈妈的人在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.83,0:09:23.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刹那 他也是组织的一员
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.13,0:09:28.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他身边就是沙慈
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.92,0:09:32.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然是一伙的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.56,0:09:34.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从那时起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.79,0:09:56.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,双推进Gundam那近乎异常的机体性能…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.72,0:09:59.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那机体究竟…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.79,0:10:10.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾纽 伊恩的伤势如何?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.12,0:10:12.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有生命危险
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.36,0:10:14.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过10天左右就可以恢复了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.90,0:10:28.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙慈·库洛斯洛特
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.27,0:10:32.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听到了露易丝的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.78,0:10:35.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来她在MS里面
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.07,0:10:40.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还喊了我的名字…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.46,0:10:44.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么 她会在A-LAWS里…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.86,0:10:49.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这还用问么…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.09,0:10:52.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为憎恨Gundam啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.48,0:10:55.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露易丝的父母 是被Gundam杀掉的!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.35,0:11:01.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是你们的错
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.80,0:11:05.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是你们的错 露易丝加入了A-LAWS…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.29,0:11:07.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后还…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.83,0:11:09.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.88,0:11:11.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.44,0:11:14.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么会变成这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.73,0:11:19.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么会变成这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.21,0:11:20.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.85,0:11:23.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是一直在这么想着
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.36,0:11:27.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要与命运抗争的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.55,0:11:31.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.04,0:11:37.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要将露易丝·哈勒维 从A-LAWS夺回来的话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.38,0:11:38.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就只有去战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.58,0:11:42.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要我去… 战斗?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.56,0:11:45.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的那么重视她的话 应该能够做到
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.03,0:11:47.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是让我去杀人么!?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.33,0:11:49.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.61,0:11:51.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是去把她夺回来的战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.59,0:11:52.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别在那里狡辩了!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.08,0:11:54.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战斗的话就会有人受伤
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.85,0:11:55.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露易丝也是…!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.06,0:11:58.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了你自己而战吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.03,0:12:04.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别开玩笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.83,0:12:06.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和你们这些人才不一样!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.70,0:12:07.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别相提并论!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.46,0:12:18.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这种癖好可不怎么好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.69,0:12:21.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不小心听到了而已
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.00,0:12:24.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 你还真的很笨啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.25,0:12:25.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.94,0:12:28.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对那个小子直说清楚不就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.00,0:12:30.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟他说「战斗由我来担下」
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.11,0:12:33.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「你去说服什么的也好」
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.39,0:12:36.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「把她从A-LAWS夺回来」
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.10,0:12:38.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并不一定会顺利
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.64,0:12:40.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 你不是已经满脑子想着要这么做了么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.37,0:12:45.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要消除过去的罪恶么?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.87,0:12:47.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是为过去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.69,0:12:48.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是为了未来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.09,0:13:08.97,Notes,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a5}发信人：露易丝·哈勒维\N　地址：RH.SK>>ΦFINE∑WAY\N　标题：写给沙慈\N\N在宇宙等我哦。\N马上就会追上你了。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.38,0:13:45.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那张照片上 是您夫人么?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.09,0:13:47.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2个月之前还是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.33,0:13:51.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被卷入KATARON的反联邦恐怖袭击死了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.66,0:14:02.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来在这里么 准尉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.45,0:14:08.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,齐宁大尉被晋升成为中佐了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.27,0:14:10.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.59,0:14:14.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在战斗途中 听到了声音
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.65,0:14:16.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,准尉 那是什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.68,0:14:18.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.89,0:14:20.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是在和敌人通话么?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.19,0:14:23.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.17,0:14:26.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 在敌人之中有准尉认识的人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.07,0:14:28.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听上去是很亲密的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.86,0:14:30.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.98,0:14:32.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些家伙是我家人的仇人!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.84,0:14:35.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是给这个世界招致不幸的人!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.02,0:14:36.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我才!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.71,0:14:39.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.39,0:14:41.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很娇嫩的手腕
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.25,0:14:43.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全不像是驾驶员应该有的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.96,0:14:47.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不应该在这A-LAWS里
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.23,0:14:52.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失礼了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.57,0:15:00.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们竟然处于人类的下风!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.49,0:15:05.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是里本斯告诉过我TWIN DRIVE的性能的话!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.59,0:15:08.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里本斯·阿尔马克?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.67,0:15:11.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布林格 听到了么?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.73,0:15:13.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,00的夺取
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.81,0:15:17.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 希林格和迪拜因竟然也被投入战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.99,0:15:22.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说 连里本斯也不清楚TWIN DRIVE的性能么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.95,0:15:26.71,Notes,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,300)}里切拉王国 军事基地
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.72,0:15:29.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 那是什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.08,0:15:30.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.75,0:15:44.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卫星兵器又发射了!?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.04,0:15:47.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 朝里切拉的军事基地
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.98,0:15:50.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要削弱中东的军力么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.04,0:15:52.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.34,0:15:56.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基地附近 应该有一个百万人规模的难民营…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.42,0:15:58.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说 也被牵连了?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.44,0:16:01.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将无罪的人们的生命夺取
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.85,0:16:03.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还在说什么世界统一!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.34,0:16:06.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用那种做法
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.65,0:16:10.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,联邦政府觉得能迎来真正的和平吗!?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.86,0:16:27.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的土地
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.01,0:16:28.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人民
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.98,0:16:29.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,国家
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.11,0:16:32.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正在消逝而去…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.54,0:16:37.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,禁言令?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.49,0:16:40.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您在说什么 司令
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.84,0:16:42.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A-LAWS使用的是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.53,0:16:44.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,利用太阳能发电
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.54,0:16:47.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从卫星轨道发射的大功率射线攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.08,0:16:50.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种大规模杀伤性武器…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.47,0:16:52.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,联邦大统领下达的特令
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.40,0:16:54.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能无视
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.59,0:16:58.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这里的士兵们全都目击了现场
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.37,0:17:00.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,言论马上会传开的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.81,0:17:03.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对A-LAWS的做法大呼不满的人也很多
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.76,0:17:06.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才拜托你担任监察一职
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.10,0:17:08.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将禁言令执行彻底
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.03,0:17:12.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是命令么? 司令
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.61,0:17:13.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.95,0:17:16.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 军方的决定不能变更
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.01,0:17:24.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要服从军纪…么…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.07,0:17:28.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲露特
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.02,0:17:30.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和王留美取得联系了?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.31,0:17:33.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 没有应答
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.99,0:17:37.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是想要卫星兵器的情报的时候…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.17,0:17:42.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卫 卫星兵器向地面发射了第二弹!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.66,0:17:43.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说什么!?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.21,0:17:45.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没时间磨磨蹭蹭了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.39,0:17:48.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斯米拉琪向全员传达
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.07,0:17:51.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托勒密号外部装甲的补修作业完成之后
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.60,0:17:53.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,立刻以TRANS-AM最大加速
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.50,0:17:57.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始攻击轨道环上的敌军卫星兵器
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.90,0:18:01.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam的补修在加速航行时也继续进行
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.61,0:18:03.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家 拜托了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.28,0:18:07.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,离开这个宙域的话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.29,0:18:08.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和露易丝就…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.46,0:18:12.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有事要拜托你 哈罗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.43,0:18:13.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么? 什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.02,0:18:21.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米蕾娜
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.33,0:18:23.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾德先生
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.89,0:18:25.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作战之前一定会修好的说
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.66,0:18:27.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.05,0:18:31.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克劳斯他…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.12,0:18:32.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战友他们都平安无事么?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.92,0:18:42.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,库洛斯洛特先生
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.00,0:18:44.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要去哪里?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.00,0:18:48.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微被人家拜托了点事…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.35,0:18:49.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜拜
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.61,0:18:51.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个人…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.51,0:18:58.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得去见她 见露易丝
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.47,0:19:01.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能呆在A-LAWS里面!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.39,0:19:05.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们明明是不相关的人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.26,0:19:07.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呆在这些地方才很奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.98,0:19:08.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战争什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.20,0:19:11.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就只让想打的家伙随便打好了!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.63,0:19:14.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们要取回来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.58,0:19:16.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些时光…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.62,0:19:18.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些日子…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.82,0:19:24.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这种转身无视现实的行为
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.40,0:19:25.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才会成为无意识的恶意
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.26,0:19:28.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,招致这样的结果
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.60,0:19:30.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夺去他们性命的人 是你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.01,0:19:32.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你那愚蠢的行为
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.89,0:19:40.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我又 要做相同的事情…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.04,0:19:43.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要怎么做…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.61,0:19:45.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要怎么做才好…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.82,0:19:47.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露易丝…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.95,0:19:57.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Cherudim Arios Seravee的各太阳炉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.21,0:20:01.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和托勒密号动力部的直接连接完成
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.56,0:20:04.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,TRANS-AM 开始!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.34,0:20:05.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,TRANS-AM!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.83,0:20:16.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托勒密号 最大出力!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.50,0:20:17.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.53,0:20:21.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…露易丝…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.30,0:20:47.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露易丝
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.42,0:22:20.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再过10分钟
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.67,0:22:24.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宇宙战舰就能到达卫星兵器的攻击可能地点
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.34,0:22:27.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这场战斗 就会决定一切啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.34,0:22:36.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要相信
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.95,0:22:37.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相信同志们
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.97,0:22:46.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卫星兵器 以光学摄像头捕捉到
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.91,0:22:48.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第2舰队的状况怎样?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.79,0:22:50.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马上就会到达指定地点
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.70,0:22:52.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.66,0:22:56.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到达之后 两支舰队利用时间差立刻开始进行导弹攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.91,0:22:59.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舰长! 卫星兵器动了!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.49,0:23:00.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说什么!?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.72,0:23:04.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,炮 炮身竟… 转到上方!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.14,0:23:08.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊! 这个角度 第2舰队吗!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.71,0:23:20.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第 第2舰队 半数被消灭!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.08,0:23:30.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第三发 发射了…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.55,0:23:32.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲露特 进行分析!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.77,0:23:33.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明 明白
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.81,0:23:37.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那兵器 也能向宇宙射击么
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.60,0:23:38.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞄准了什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.09,0:23:42.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,KATARON的宇宙舰队
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.48,0:23:43.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么!?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.16,0:23:45.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这帮杂种…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.40,0:23:52.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是联邦的…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.55,0:23:54.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.71,0:23:56.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,变革者的做法
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.33,0:24:02.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卫星兵器理应破坏
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.45,0:24:05.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天行者执行决死任务
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.54,0:24:09.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集 Memento-Mori攻略战
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.08,0:24:13.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这正是 Gundam机师的神髓
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
